<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM4.3.9">
<l>kaḷaṅkaṉi vaṇṇā kaṇṇaṇē yeṉṟaṉ kārmuki lēyeṉa niṉaintiṭ</l>
<l>ṭuḷaṅkaṉin tirukku maṭiyavar taṅka ḷuḷḷattu  ḷūṟiya tēṉai</l>
<l>teḷintanāṉ maṟaiyōr nāṅkainaṉ ṉaṭuvuḷcempoṉcey kōyili ṉuḷḷē</l>
<l>vaḷaṅkoḷpē riṉpam maṉṉiniṉ ṟāṉai vaṇaṅkināṉ vāḻntoḻin tēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Having bowed to the one who remains abounding in great delight</l>
<l rend="indent">which brings prosperity,</l>
<l>Within the Cempoṉcey Temple right in the center of Nāṅkai</l>
<l rend="indent">with experts of the four Vedas, which are clear,</l>
<l>The honey which flows into the hearts of devotees whose hearts keep melting,</l>
<l>Firmly thinking, “You the hue of blueberries, Kaṇṇaṉ, my own dark cloud,”</l>
<l rend="indent">living [happily], I was at ease.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
